gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 120, Trail Blazers 107
gameRecap.excerpt: Kevin Durant (31 points, nine assists) and Devin Booker (28 points, six assists) combine for 59 points to lead the Suns past the Trail Blazers, 120-107.  Jerami Grant tallied 26 points, four rebounds and six assists for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Suns improve to 8-6, 2-1 in IST, while the Trail Blazers fall to 3-11, 1-3 in IST play.
